comments: Capela (ATL) applies a legal hand to Nurkic's (POR) body in the post and he absorbs the contact.
Capela (ATL) maintains verticality and legally contests Nurkic's (POR) shot near the rim.
Nurkic (POR) is already in Wright's (ATL) path and he brings his arms slightly forward as he releases away from the contact.
Little (POR) moves into Young's (ATL) body and initiates contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Powell (POR) and Wright (ATL) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Simons (POR) is bracing for the contact from Huerter (ATL) as he releases away from the contact.
Gallinari (ATL) is already in Little's (POR) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Nurkic (POR) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Young (ATL) that affects his driving shot attempt.
Gallinari (ATL) makes contact with Nurkic's (POR) arm as he defends the shot near the rim.
Powell (POR) brushes Young's (ATL) arm, causing Young to momentarily lose control of the ball, which he quickly recovers.
Little (POR) legally contests Gallinari's (ATL) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Huerter (ATL) commits a take foul on Simons (POR).
Capela (ATL) is already in Powell's (POR) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Nance Jr.(POR) inbounds the ball within five seconds.
Gallinari (ATL) commits a take foul on Simons (POR).
